/* ── Spirit OS globals - minimal @theme + Tailwind v4 import ─────────────────
 * > Turbopack/PostCSS was eating glass on this tree; keep @theme flat, fewer @apply.
 * > Accents + ThemeEngine: _blueprints/design_system.md
